        public void setOpenByInputClick(boolean openByClickOnInput)
        Sets opening of select. Default open method is by clicking on the input.
        Parameters:
        openByClickOnInput - if true, select will be opened by input clicking (default). If false, the select will be opened by 'show' button of the select.
